OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,6,FCloudier on Wednesday with some patchy
OL,7,Frain. Thursday and Friday, mostly dry
OL,8,Fwith bright or sunny spells. Turning
OL,9,Fvery warm, perhaps locally hot, and
OL,10,Ffeeling increasingly humid. Thundery
OL,11,Fshowers possible.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
